{"tid":2238571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吉爾吉斯政局動盪：親中親俄總統被轟下台　中國「一帶一路」烏雲籠罩","createTime":"2020-10-11T08:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T08:54:52.000Z","uid":261647,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cd6af22340d2c44dd99a04b075bdf7b65331731f","tid":2238571,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T08:54:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TaiwaneseLocalismFront/photos/a.338575123170266/1224818401212596/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTaiwaneseLocalismFront%2Fphotos%2Fa.338575123170266%2F1224818401212596%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=ee283bf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TaiwaneseLocalismFront/photos/a.338575123170266/1224818401212596/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUG9xNO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUG9xNO.jpg&h=c63afb8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「出外打工國」固然坐擁著眾多華麗敘事（史詩），#足以免費攀附（未必相干於目前的自己），但是卻「照例」深陷於族群問題、南北對立、認同錯亂等因情。活在世界島的核心深處內裡，保證是麻煩不斷 💯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/article/3098236\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Farticle%2F3098236&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=d4642dbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/article/3098236</a><br />\n<br />\n姑且揣摩看看：實際上自認為他自己是世俗主義者的無宗無派穆斯林（黎巴嫩和高加索地區也很多），#用西里爾字母表記阿拉伯語經文當人森指南（僅供偶而參考之用），親戚在莫斯科打工、長輩於蘇聯紅軍服役，但是自己（開公司承包米軍基地業務：非得學好美語）看起來又跟中囶境內的親戚（他們倒是沿用阿拉伯字母表記書面體）很像，#這可比台灣的狀況麻煩太多太多太多了 💔<br />\n<br />\n相對說來台灣還比較單純些（✅）<br />\n起碼本島的海岸線邊界明確（✅）<br />\n而且宗教問題幾乎不是問題（✅）<br />\n要是活在世界島深處超麻煩（🚫）<br />\n下面有一堆精彩圖片慢慢逛（✅）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8663/4919336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.udn.com%2Fglobal_vision%2Fstory%2F8663%2F4919336&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=f46ff94f\" target=\"_blank\">https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8663/4919336</a>"}]}